  <brief_title>MOSAIC - Multicenter International Study of Oxaliplatin/ 5FU-LV in the Adjuvant Treatment of Colon Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Multicenter International Study of Oxaliplatin/ 5FU-LV in the Adjuvant Treatment of Colon Cancer</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Sanofi</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Sanofi</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the FOLFOX regimen versus LV5FU2 in the adjuvant treatment of stage II and III
      colon cancer.

      Primary objective: Disease Free Survival (DFS) Secondary objective: Overall Survival (OS),
      safety (including long term toxicity)
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
